{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01SBGF5oB3T7QvJM578qVADM","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Migration complete. Here is the full summary:\n\n---\n\n### Migration Summary\n\n- **Frameworks:** Jakarta EE 10 (Open Liberty) -> Quarkus 3.8.4\n- **Key actions:** Replaced EJBs with CDI beans, JSF with JAX-RS REST endpoints, EclipseLink with Hibernate ORM, Liberty config with Quarkus application.properties\n- **Overall outcome:** SUCCESS - Application builds, starts, and passes all 10 smoke tests\n\n### File Tree\n\n```\nModified:\n- pom.xml: Complete rewrite for Quarkus BOM, dependencies, and build plugins\n- Dockerfile: Updated for Quarkus fast-jar deployment\n- src/main/java/.../entity/CustomerOrder.java: Added @JsonIgnore for serialization safety\n- src/main/java/.../entity/LineItem.java: Added @JsonIgnore annotations\n- src/main/java/.../entity/Part.java: Added @JsonIgnore annotations\n- src/main/java/.../entity/Vendor.java: Added @JsonIgnore, fixed NPE in constructor\n- src/main/java/.../entity/VendorPart.java: Added @JsonIgnore annotations\n- src/main/java/.../ejb/RequestBean.java: @Stateful EJB -> @ApplicationScoped CDI + @Transactional\n- src/main/java/.../ejb/ConfigBean.java: @Singleton EJB -> @ApplicationScoped + @Observes StartupEvent\n- src/main/java/.../web/OrderManager.java: JSF @Named -> JAX-RS @Path REST resource\n\nAdded:\n- src/main/resources/application.properties: Quarkus H2/Hibernate config\n- smoke.py: 10 REST API smoke tests\n- CHANGELOG.md: Full migration documentation\n\nRemoved:\n- src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml\n- src/main/liberty/config/server.xml\n- src/main/webapp/ (all XHTML templates, web.xml, CSS)\n```\n\n### Step-by-Step Log\n\n```\n[2026-03-17T01:10:00Z] [info] Analyzed project structure - Jakarta EE 10 with JSF/EJB/JPA\n[2026-03-17T01:12:00Z] [info] Rewrote pom.xml with Quarkus 3.8.4 dependencies\n[2026-03-17T01:14:00Z] [info] Created application.pro